Sudah ditolong belum?

19
00:01:59,100 --> 00:02:01,060
Nyonya, jangan panik,
Tuan Besar sudah ditolong.

20
00:02:01,320 --> 00:02:02,740
Sudah kami antar ke gedung utama.

21
00:02:02,840 --> 00:02:03,610
Bagus kalau begitu.

22
